Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:20.89,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Why not 闘い得た　絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:29.52,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Just now　この手の中で　熱く輝け
