Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:47.76,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Someday 世界が終わる日が　来たって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:52.96,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}So，What？　1ミリの悔いもない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:58.68,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Say， yeah！！　一筋に走る流れ星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:01.34,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}鼓動ドキドキ止まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:06.09,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}迷いも全部　蹴っ飛ばせ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:11.61,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}宇宙に　抱かれし　蒼い地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:16.88,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}いつも心に描く　エリシオン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:22.24,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}過去も未来も　自分が創る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:27.50,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}永遠の“Stellar”を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:32.97,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}“命のうた”が聞こえる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:58.01,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義の剣は折れ 無機質に転がった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:03.38,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支えてた自分 reasonとか 見えなくなってしまうの?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:08.55,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手で掴んでも 右手からこぼれて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:13.64,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣いてなんかいないのに 霞んで行く情景
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.80,0:22:18.93,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ゆらり揺れて 惑わす世界はきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:23.39,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来切符を探してる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:29.44,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈍い音に 焦らされるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:33.62,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走り出さなきゃ ゴールはない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.84,0:22:39.94,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,future is serious! future is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:45.35,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんで、どうして、心が邪魔をするの?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:47.72,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,future is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:57.13,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何十回繰り返しても 戸惑いを振り払って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:23:07.21,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立ち上がる まだ夢を見たまま…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,bt,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)}第5話 「蓋諾斯城的{\1c&537ea3&}秘{\1c&HFFFFFF&}密」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請 請快點投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得漂亮 美莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你 女王軍便所向無敵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為操控超振動鎧甲的先驅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遲早會被大家交口稱讚的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:01:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也要好好表現哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/OP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.27,0:02:39.41,bt,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(140,0)}第6話 「{\1c&4a3db3&}花{\1c&HFFFFFF&}環與隱藏的力量」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被大家稱讚…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美莉姆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我幫您搓背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會幫您按摩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了 我自己能洗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼客氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾 我也要來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 快要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天美莉姆大人也很威風凜凜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都以能和美莉姆大人並肩戰鬥為榮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也請多多關照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫迪 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.62,0:04:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然反力場還是沒有起動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪裡出錯了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早的吵什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的那套
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得要與美莉姆的鎧甲對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能靠反超振動鎧甲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不管怎麼弄 就是形成不了力場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美莉姆一邊忍受著這種振動一邊戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這樣會給身體帶來很大負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理論應該沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是魔導石的純度不夠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.36,0:05:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 再試一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 怎麼回事 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 差點忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽村民們說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫美莉姆的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著剛才那樣的鎧甲對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠她一個 就攻陷了這附近的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頗有些名聲了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠她一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美莉姆怎可能做出那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明明那麼溫柔善良
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是聽來的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是因為鎧甲的力量而無法控制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美莉姆 快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣 站在女王那一邊就是敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一起收拾掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁著這個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決不要和美莉姆戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對 不行的啊 和美莉姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和美莉姆…戰鬥什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把那力量收為己用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優米爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這個麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓侍從給你送過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有收到媽媽的回信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時還沒收到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必令堂也忙於日常生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你好好表現 令堂也會欣慰的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要想太多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天要回蓋諾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就作為護衛跟著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在 我也安心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山茶花的花語是「強大與驕傲」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花環的做法 是你教會我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤依特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美莉姆 一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然明白你為了媽媽和弟弟們很需要錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:09:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但勉強自己去戰鬥 誰都不會為此高興
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優米爾大人會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我並不喜歡戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但優米爾大人期待著我的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我知道是多虧了這件鎧甲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是第一次聽到這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次被別人需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優米爾只是利用你而已 你被優米爾騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優米爾大人對我很親切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還幫我把錢和信送給媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且呢 我只是把違抗女王大人的人收拾掉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是做什麼壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美莉姆 你在哪啊美莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 理解我 尤依特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美莉姆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值班守衛看到了可疑的人影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有看到什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 優米爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這裡的花做的 想送給優米爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見到那樣的美莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的臉上充滿了自信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想到「啊 美莉姆變強了呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此玩弄美莉姆感情的優米爾 絕對不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 依靠鎧甲來戰鬥 並不是真正的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想救美莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有什麼辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞那鎧甲的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等姐姐快被打倒的時候 就出手救她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要受姐姐表揚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話姐姐就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請 請投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽尤依特說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒可能的 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了戰鬥別無選擇！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快點 逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快點投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點救姐姐才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 溫迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搶回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跑？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有 就沒有什麼破壞盔甲的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是魔導石的純度不夠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 魔導石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐竟然像我一樣變身了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人好帥 好剛強～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不阻止她的話美莉姆就要被…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 美莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有它在手膽壯壯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 還給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換主人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優米爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞掉的實驗品對我沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機器人喲 大發神威吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫迪 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海盜美學之三
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷸蚌相爭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漁翁得利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住 你這強盜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這機器人是屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:21:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是女王軍直屬 鋼鐵參謀‧優米爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下來 還不放我們下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所願
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼各位 再會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫迪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.08,0:23:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明最強鬥士計劃只差一點點就要成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪安妮洛特 精心打造的超振動鎧甲毀於一旦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.49,0:23:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 她那不可思議的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大概是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.68,0:23:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看來戰略需要做一點改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 翱翔天際的海盜船
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有船長‧莉莉安娜來礙事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那機器人已經是我的囊中之物了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.30,0:23:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那所謂的海盜美學 讓我好好見識下吧


